data.description: Sellers has a VA assumable loan at 2.75%.  Welcome to the epitome of luxury living! The Saint Albans model in our esteemed community offers an unparalleled level of elegance and space, with a massive 8400 square feet of finished living area. Nestled on a private cul-de-sac and sprawling over 2 acres of lush land, this home provides the utmost privacy and tranquility.  As you approach, you'll be impressed by the sophisticated brick facade that exudes timeless charm and durability. The convenience of a spacious 3-car side load garage ensures ample parking for your vehicles and guests.  Step inside, and you'll be greeted by impeccable landscaping that complements the natural beauty of the surroundings, as the property backs onto a serene wooded area.  The interior of this home leaves nothing to be desired. Boasting 5 generously-sized bedrooms and 4.5 bathrooms, it comfortably accommodates a large family or visiting guests. The primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a generous sitting room, two walk-in closets, and a luxurious primary bath complete with dual sinks, a separate shower, a soaking tub, and a water closet.  Bedroom #2 enjoys the convenience of its own en-suite full bathroom, while bedrooms #3 and #4 are connected by a well-appointed jack and jill bathroom.  Designed to cater to all your needs, this home offers ample space for various activities and entertaining. With an office, a living room, a dining room complemented by a butler's pantry, a cozy family room with a fireplace, a side sunroom, and a morning room off the kitchen, there's no shortage of gathering areas.  The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring custom cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances, offering both beauty and functionality.  Venturing downstairs, you'll find a fully finished basement that presents a recreation area, bedroom #5, a full bathroom, a theater room for entertainment enthusiasts, a bar for hosting guests, as well as a washer and dryer for convenience. Plenty of storage space ensures you have room for all your belongings.  Outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the large maintenance-free deck at the rear of the home, perfect for enjoying the fresh air and hosting gatherings.  Additional features include an irrigation system for easy lawn maintenance and an extra parking pad off the driveway, providing even more parking capacity.  Overall, this rare Saint Albans model in the Saint James community is a harmonious blend of luxury, space, and seclusion. Meticulously maintained, this home presents a remarkable opportunity for those seeking a distinctive, well-appointed, and high-quality residence. With its unbeatable location and exceptional features, it truly is a sanctuary of comfort and style. Don't miss this chance – schedule a showing today!
